channel.title: Rspslist V2 - Rsps Toplist & Community
channel.description:
Hello, RSPSlist is a RSPS community, we are here to help RSPS developers.
Well, we are a community. We want to grow, since we have spend alot of time to code things, we have recoded the website a few times now :/ We never became big. So now when we have released "V2", we will try all we can to make it big! Some of you probably already knows Rspslist, because we have been here before. About 6 months ago. We started this project for about 1 year ago. This website was made from scratch, by me. Everything is made by me on the site, but not the reCaptcha.
Some features:
[ul][*][color=#130a41][B]Webclient Hosting[/B][/COLOR] [*][color=#130a41][B]Signature Maker[/B][/COLOR] [*][color=#130a41][B]Status Checker[/B][/COLOR] [*][color=#130a41][B]Notifications[/B][/COLOR] [*][color=#130a41][B]Friendship system[/B][/COLOR] [*][color=#130a41][B]User Profiles[/B][/COLOR] [*][color=#130a41][B]Items List (23k+ items)[/B][/COLOR] [*][color=#130a41][B]Objects List (65k+ objects)[/B][/COLOR] [*][color=#130a41][B]Npcs List (14k+ npcs)[/B][/COLOR] [*][color=#130a41][B]Forum[/B][/COLOR] [*][color=#130a41][B]Toplist[/B][/COLOR] [*][color=#130a41][B]ChatBox[/B][/COLOR] [*][color=#130a41][B]Voting[/B][/COLOR] [*][color=#130a41][B]AND ALSO MORE![/B][/COLOR]
--Links-- [URL=http://bit.ly/OJKhNd]Website[/URL]
Credits: Zerak - [Developer/Founder]
Pictures: My own-made shoutbox. [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/MM0Qz.png[/img] My own-made forum. [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/h6CnL.png[/img] Rspslist Stats: [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/ikkfj.png[/img] Toplist: [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/OjyA9.png[/img] Users: [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/3p8Ac.png[/img] Notifications: [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/6TXxq.png[/img] Tools: [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/Ap4Bv.png[/img]
